Movie producer Omoni Oboli has stated she was not born wealthy. She recalled how her mother, a single parent, struggled financially to fend for herself and siblings. She however said if she could make it, others too can succeeed regardless of their current predicaments. Oboli wrote: “I wasn’t born with a silver spoon! My earliest memories were in a face -me -I -face- you- home. Raised by a single mom.   Don Jazzy, ex-wife meet     Video streaming platform Accelerate plus launched     Toyin Adekeye’s Bigger Than Africa set for Netflix debut   “We always had more months left at the end of the money every single month Our mom had multiple hustles in addition to her teaching job just to make ends meet. “I never visited the airport not to talk of travelling outside Nigeria as a kid “If I can get to where I am today, YOU CAN Truth is, I’m just getting started. You don’t have to like me but I Will motivate you to success.”